<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Activate Your Account</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background-color: #fff;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello <%= user.name %>,</h2>

        <p>Thank you for registering with us!</p>
        <p>Please click the button below to activate your account. This link will expire in 5 minutes.</p>

        <a class="btn" href="<%= activationLink %>">Activate Account</a>

        <p>If the button doesnâ€™t work, you can also copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
        <p><a href="<%= activationLink %>"><%= activationLink %></a></p>

        <p><strong>Activation Code:</strong> <%= activationCode %></p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Company Name. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
